	(text "SOFT CARD: ISA bus + power ONLY. Self-decodes 0xA0000-0xBFFFF and 3B4/3B5/3B8/3BA/3BF + 3D4/3D5/3D8/3D9/3DA from snooped A17-A19/A0-A9. No Y5, no link, no host RAM (design S8). Straps: JP1 open = card disabled (firmware keeps all OEs off); JP2 = CGA (closed) / MDA (open) window set."
		(at 38.1 20.32 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "8ea30d0d-372d-564b-9639-445cdc89c597")
	)
	(text "HDMI: +5V fused (F1); HPD sensed on GPIO41. Add TMDS ESD array (TPD4E05U06-class, <=0.15pF) at layout -- no KiCad symbol yet."
		(at 266.7 33.02 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "2911307a-3ccb-5d9a-af6d-d6c0b48daf75")
	)
	(text "Standalone Video PCB: ISA bus chains J_IN -> J_OUT; card logic taps the bus by name. Daisy-chain cards header-to-header (isa_conn, S4.3)."
		(at 38.1 12.7 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "23ff70fa-3099-5d88-9312-d442b407f156")
	)
